As used in this section:
"Agreement" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010;
"Approved company" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010;
"Economic development project" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010;
"Electronic processing" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010;
"Equipment" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010;
"Project term" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010; and
"Research and development" has the same meaning as in KRS 154.31-010.
